# OnceUponATime record image example
# This uses a generic user-defined record, not a renderer-specific Vec3 primitive.

Once upon a time.

Define the record Vec3 with x number and y number and z number.
The color is a Vec3 with x 1 and y 0.5 and z 0.25.

Create image canvas with width 1 and height 1.
Paint canvas at 0 0 with color x, color y, color z.
Save image canvas to "output/record_color.ppm".

The story ends.
